Box 5, 202 South First Street, Ste 1, LaGrange, KY 40031 Office Hours are 8:30 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 37575=Copyright © 2015, 23338=Molly Malone enjoys the simple things: spending time with family, a Sunday afternoon nap and quality time with her chew toys. Outside of her ordinary life, though, this 9-year-old Labrador retriever is being feted as a hero by local animal welfare groups. It was 2:45 a.m. on Nov. 2, when the clickity-clack of Molly’s nails on the hardwood floor woke her owner, Joe Malone. This was not unusual; Molly wakes Joe most nights when she needs to go outside.}
